Att.txtRmkWorkHr: Activation can be checked pre-flight with Steenokkerzeel ATCC (TEL +32 (0) 2 443 82 04).

Ase.txtRmk: Air exercises and RPAS flights. During RPAS activity, prohibited to all manned aircraft. Other traffic may be allowed inside the TSA for transit purposes. At all times the standard radar separation minima must be maintained between the RPAS and the other traffic, therefore the manned aircraft flying within this TSA must be under radar control.
